title: Four migrants in critical condition after Calais shooting
text:
Four migrants in critical condition after Calais shooting 1:03pm GMT - 00:49 
A brawl between Eritrean and Afghan migrants in the French port city of Calais has resulted in four critical injuries from gunshot wounds. The port has born the brunt of France's migrant crisis. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
